Title: The Trial of Style
Description:
Well, that's certainly an... interesting look, $c.

Me? Judgmental? Certainly not. However, I'm curious what others would think of it.

You should speak to the Transmogrifier over there and enter the Trial of Style.

We'll see what public opinion says about your choice in garb.
ObjectivesText: Speak to a Transmogrifier to enter and complete the Trial of Style.
